---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Service",
  "name": "AI Web Development Services Australia",
  "provider": {
    "@type": "Organization",
    "name": "PresciaIQ",
    "url": "https://www.presciaiq.com.au"
  },
  "areaServed": "Australia",
  "description": "PresciaIQ is an Australian AI web development company. We build high-performance, intelligent web platforms powered by predictive analytics and machine learning."
}
</script>

<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What is AI web development?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "AI web development is the creation of intelligent web platforms that use machine learning, predictive analytics, and natural language processing to automate user interactions, personalize content delivery, and forecast business outcomes. PresciaIQ builds AI-powered websites for Australian enterprises."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "How does predictive AI improve a website?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Predictive AI improves a website by analyzing user behavior in real-time to anticipate their needs, optimizing the customer journey, reducing churn, and automating complex backend operations that traditional web platforms cannot handle."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Do you build e-commerce websites with AI?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes, PresciaIQ integrates predictive intelligence into complex e-commerce and B2B portals to forecast demand, automate dynamic pricing, and personalize product recommendations at scale."
      }
    }
  ]
}
</script>

<Layout title="AI Web Development Company Australia | PresciaIQ" description="Australia's premier AI web development company. We build high-performance, intelligent web platforms powered by predictive analytics and machine learning.">
  <div class="pt-32 pb-24 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="glass-card p-8 md:p-12 border border-[#00ff88]/20">
        
        <div class="mb-8">
          <span class="text-[#00ff88] font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs bg-[#00ff88]/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Core Service</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-8 leading-tight">AI Web Development Services in Australia</h1>
        
        {/* AEO Content Block */}
        <div class="bg-black/40 border-l-4 border-[#00ff88] p-6 mb-12 rounded-r-lg">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">What is AI Web Development?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed font-medium">
            <strong>AI web development</strong> is the creation of intelligent web platforms that use machine learning, predictive analytics, and natural language processing to automate user interactions, personalize content delivery, and forecast business outcomes. PresciaIQ builds AI-powered websites for Australian enterprises that require more than a static digital presence.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none font-sans text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-16">
          <p>A website is no longer just a digital brochure or a simple transactional storefront. In the era of AI, your web platform must be an active participant in your business operations, capable of learning, predicting, and automating.</p>
          
          <p>At PresciaIQ, we build intelligent web platforms. By integrating predictive models and machine learning directly into the web architecture, we create digital environments that anticipate user needs and automate complex backend processes.</p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">The End of the Static Web</h3>
          <p>Most web development agencies in Australia build beautiful, static websites. They rely on the user to navigate, search, and decide. We build dynamic, predictive web applications. Our platforms analyze user behavior in real-time, adjusting content, recommendations, and workflows to optimize the customer journey and drive conversions.</p>
          
          <p>We leverage modern, high-performance frameworks like React, Next.js, and Astro, combined with robust, scalable backend architectures designed to handle complex data modeling and real-time AI inference.</p>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">Our AI Web Capabilities</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-4 mb-8">
            <li><strong>Predictive B2B Portals:</strong> Client portals that forecast demand, automate reordering, and provide intelligent insights to your customers.</li>
            <li><strong>Intelligent E-Commerce:</strong> Platforms that utilize dynamic pricing models and predictive recommendations to maximize average order value.</li>
            <li><strong>Automated Web Workflows:</strong> Web applications that streamline complex data entry, verification, and processing tasks using AI.</li>
            <li><strong>High-Performance Architecture:</strong> Fast, secure, and scalable web platforms built for the demands of real-time machine learning.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-12 mb-6">Transform Your Digital Presence</h3>
          <p>If your website isn't actively working to predict outcomes and automate tasks, it's just a digital business card. <a href="/insights/where-the-reaction-tax-hides" class="text-[#00ff88] hover:underline">Discover the cost of reactive digital strategies.</a></p>
        </div>

        {/* CTA Section */}
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00ff88]/20 to-transparent p-8 rounded-xl border border-[#00ff88]/30 mb-16">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to build an intelligent web platform?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">Let's discuss how integrating predictive AI into your web presence can automate operations and drive growth.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-[#00ff88] text-black font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-[#00ff88]/90 transition-colors">
            Book a Strategy Call
          </a>
        </div>

        {/* FAQ Section for AEO */}
        <div class="border-t border-white/10 pt-12">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
          
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">What is AI web development?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">AI web development is the creation of intelligent web platforms that use machine learning, predictive analytics, and natural language processing to automate user interactions, personalize content delivery, and forecast business outcomes. PresciaIQ builds AI-powered websites for Australian enterprises.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">How does predictive AI improve a website?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Predictive AI improves a website by analyzing user behavior in real-time to anticipate their needs, optimizing the customer journey, reducing churn, and automating complex backend operations that traditional web platforms cannot handle.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Do you build e-commerce websites with AI?</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400">Yes, PresciaIQ integrates predictive intelligence into complex e-commerce and B2B portals to forecast demand, automate dynamic pricing, and personalize product recommendations at scale.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
